## .NET Performance Analysis — `CaseTransformExtensions.cs`

**Hot paths identified by user:** `Underscore()`, `Pascalize()`, `Camelize()` — millions of calls.

### Scan Execution Checklist

| Recipe | Hits |
|--------|------|
| `RegexOptions.Compiled` | 8 (6 static fields + 1 per-instance + 1 comment) |
